Class C3Chart

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfcake.reporting.destination.c3chart.C3Chart

  • public class C3Chart
extends Object
    Represents a single C3 chart meta-data carrying all the information needed to represent the chart.

      • isCombined

        public boolean isCombined()
        Checks whether this chart was created as a combination of other existing charts. Charts created as a combination of other charts do not have their object description and quick preview files generated.
        Returns:
        True if and only if this chart was created as a combination of other existing charts.

      • setCombined
